"{\"uid\": \"breitbart.com-sports-2024-07-28-bishop-robert-barron-olympics-apology-last-supper-parody-anything-but-apology\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Minnesota Bishop Robert Barron described a statement from the organizers of the 2024 Paris Olympics, apologizing for an LGBTQ parody of the \\\"Last Supper\\\" during the opening ceremony, as \\\"anything but an apology.\\\"\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 212, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 0, \"end\": 9, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Minnesota\", \"score\": 0.9989511841982558, \"rank\": 0.001009548551340226, \"text\": \"Minnesota\", \"types\": [\"Q3455524\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Minnesota\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Minnesota\"}, {\"begin\": 17, \"end\": 30, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Robert_Barron\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.502102608967128e-19, \"text\": \"Robert Barron\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Robert_Barron\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Robert_Barron\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In avideoposted to X, Barron criticized an apology from the organizers of the Olympics regarding\\u00a0a mocking LGBTQ parody of the \\\"Last Supper\\\" that featured Barbara Butch, a DJ, producer, and LGBTQ activist in the middle, while drag queens and transgender performers were seen on either side of her.\", \"from\": 214, \"to\": 511, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 236, \"end\": 242, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Family_of_Donald_Trump\", \"score\": 0.9999999956100964, \"rank\": 4.388505894091456e-09, \"text\": \"Barron\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Family_of_Donald_Trump\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Family_of_Donald_Trump\"}, {\"begin\": 369, \"end\": 382, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Barbara_Butch\", \"score\": 0.9999897744159937, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Barbara Butch\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Barbara_Butch\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Barbara_Butch\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Barron said the Olympics organizer's \\\"so-called apology\\\" was \\\"patronizing\\\" and \\\"condescending\\\" towards Christians and unapologetic about the actual offense committed against them.\", \"from\": 512, \"to\": 691, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 512, \"end\": 518, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Family_of_Donald_Trump\", \"score\": 0.9999999956100964, \"rank\": 4.388505894091456e-09, \"text\": \"Barron\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Family_of_Donald_Trump\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Family_of_Donald_Trump\"}, {\"begin\": 615, \"end\": 625, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\", \"score\": 0.5790939635615081, \"rank\": 0.7240176681261816, \"text\": \"Christians\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The bishop's video came after he previously posted a video on X,criticizingthe drag queen parody of the \\\"Last Supper\\\" as being a \\\"gross, sort of flippant mockery\\\"\\u00a0of the faith of Christians around the world.\", \"from\": 693, \"to\": 900, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 872, \"end\": 882, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\", \"score\": 0.5790939635615081, \"rank\": 0.7240176681261816, \"text\": \"Christians\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I saw the so-called, apology from the organizing committee, and I thought, 'It's anything but an apology,'\\\" Barron said in his video.\", \"from\": 902, \"to\": 1036, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1011, \"end\": 1017, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Family_of_Donald_Trump\", \"score\": 0.9999999956100964, \"rank\": 4.388505894091456e-09, \"text\": \"Barron\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Family_of_Donald_Trump\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Family_of_Donald_Trump\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"In fact, it's kind of a masterpiece of woke duplicity.\\\"\", \"from\": 1037, \"to\": 1093, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Barron added that he \\\"wanted to say a few things\\\" in response to the apology, adding that if the organizers thought the apology would \\\"mollify Christians\\\" they should \\\"think again.\\\"\", \"from\": 1095, \"to\": 1276, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1095, \"end\": 1101, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Family_of_Donald_Trump\", \"score\": 0.9999999956100964, \"rank\": 4.388505894091456e-09, \"text\": \"Barron\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Family_of_Donald_Trump\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Family_of_Donald_Trump\"}, {\"begin\": 1238, \"end\": 1248, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\", \"score\": 0.5790939635615081, \"rank\": 0.7240176681261816, \"text\": \"Christians\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Here's some of the things that were said,\\\" Barron continued, reading as he quoted directly from the Olympic organizers' statement.\", \"from\": 1278, \"to\": 1409, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1322, \"end\": 1328, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Family_of_Donald_Trump\", \"score\": 0.9999999956100964, \"rank\": 4.388505894091456e-09, \"text\": \"Barron\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Family_of_Donald_Trump\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Family_of_Donald_Trump\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"'Clearly, there was never an intention to show disrespect to any religious group,' give me a break.\", \"from\": 1410, \"to\": 1510, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"So, we have a group of drag queens cavorting in a kind of sexually provocative way.\", \"from\": 1511, \"to\": 1594, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Clearly, an imitation of da Vinci's Last Supper.\\\"\", \"from\": 1595, \"to\": 1644, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Anne Descamps, a spokesperson for the 2024 Paris Olympics had said in a statement that there was \\\"never an intention to show disrespect to any religious group,\\\" and that they had tried to \\\"celebrate community tolerance.\\\"\", \"from\": 1646, \"to\": 1866, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1651, \"end\": 1659, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jean-Baptiste_Descamps\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Descamps\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jean-Baptiste_Descamps\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jean-Baptiste_Descamps\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Clearly there was never an intention to show disrespect to any religious group,\\\" Descamps said in the statement.\", \"from\": 1868, \"to\": 1981, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1950, \"end\": 1958, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jean-Baptiste_Descamps\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Descamps\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jean-Baptiste_Descamps\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jean-Baptiste_Descamps\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"On the contrary, I think [with] Thomas Jolly, we really did try to celebrate community tolerance.\", \"from\": 1982, \"to\": 2080, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Looking at the result of the polls that we shared, we believe that this ambition was achieved.\", \"from\": 2081, \"to\": 2175, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"If people have taken offense we are, of course, really, really sorry.\\\"\", \"from\": 2176, \"to\": 2246, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Barron continued to criticize the apology, \\\"I love this, 'We tried to celebrate community tolerance.'\", \"from\": 2248, \"to\": 2349, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2248, \"end\": 2254, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Family_of_Donald_Trump\", \"score\": 0.9999999956100964, \"rank\": 4.388505894091456e-09, \"text\": \"Barron\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Family_of_Donald_Trump\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Family_of_Donald_Trump\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Yeah, tolerance.\", \"from\": 2350, \"to\": 2366, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Except, for those pesky 2.6 billion Christians on the planet, everyone's welcome, everyone's tolerated.\", \"from\": 2367, \"to\": 2470, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2403, \"end\": 2413, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\", \"score\": 0.5790939635615081, \"rank\": 0.7240176681261816, \"text\": \"Christians\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"All this lovely diversity, until you get to anyone that disagrees with your ideology, like these 2.6 billion people.\", \"from\": 2471, \"to\": 2587, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"So, do not give me this business about tolerance and diversity.\\\"\", \"from\": 2588, \"to\": 2652, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"And then, 'We believe this ambition celebrating tolerance was achieved,'\\\" Barron added.\", \"from\": 2654, \"to\": 2742, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2729, \"end\": 2735, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Family_of_Donald_Trump\", \"score\": 0.9999999956100964, \"rank\": 4.388505894091456e-09, \"text\": \"Barron\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Family_of_Donald_Trump\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Family_of_Donald_Trump\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Well, I wonder what planet they are living on if they think harmony and peace and all this was achieved by this clear affront to Christians.\", \"from\": 2743, \"to\": 2884, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2873, \"end\": 2883, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\", \"score\": 0.5790939635615081, \"rank\": 0.7240176681261816, \"text\": \"Christians\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And, then at the very end, a standard bit of condescension, 'If people have taken any offense, we are truly sorry.'\", \"from\": 2885, \"to\": 3000, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"In other words, if you are so simple-minded and stupid to have been offended by this wonderful expression of French culture, well, you know, we are sorry about that.\\\"\", \"from\": 3001, \"to\": 3167, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3110, \"end\": 3124, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Culture_of_France\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"French culture\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Culture_of_France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Culture_of_France\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The bishop added that Christians were offended by the display \\\"because it was offensive.\\\"\", \"from\": 3169, \"to\": 3258, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3191, \"end\": 3201, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\", \"score\": 0.5790939635615081, \"rank\": 0.7240176681261816, \"text\": \"Christians\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Please do not patronize us with this condescending remark about well, 'If you had any bad feelings, we are awfully sorry about that,'\\\" Barron added.\", \"from\": 3260, \"to\": 3409, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3396, \"end\": 3402, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Family_of_Donald_Trump\", \"score\": 0.9999999956100964, \"rank\": 4.388505894091456e-09, \"text\": \"Barron\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Family_of_Donald_Trump\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Family_of_Donald_Trump\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Barron encouraged Christians to not give up and to continue to make their voices heard.\", \"from\": 3411, \"to\": 3498, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3411, \"end\": 3417, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Family_of_Donald_Trump\", \"score\": 0.9999999956100964, \"rank\": 4.388505894091456e-09, \"text\": \"Barron\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Family_of_Donald_Trump\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Family_of_Donald_Trump\"}, {\"begin\": 3429, \"end\": 3439, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\", \"score\": 0.5790939635615081, \"rank\": 0.7240176681261816, \"text\": \"Christians\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"A real apology would be something like, 'This was a mistake, it should never have been done, and we are sorry for it,'\\\" Barron said, adding that Christians should not be mollified, but \\\"should keep raising\\\" their voices.\", \"from\": 3499, \"to\": 3720, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3620, \"end\": 3626, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Family_of_Donald_Trump\", \"score\": 0.9999999956100964, \"rank\": 4.388505894091456e-09, \"text\": \"Barron\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Family_of_Donald_Trump\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Family_of_Donald_Trump\"}, {\"begin\": 3645, \"end\": 3655, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\", \"score\": 0.5790939635615081, \"rank\": 0.7240176681261816, \"text\": \"Christians\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Pleaselet us knowif you are having issues with commenting.\", \"from\": 3722, \"to\": 3780, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Copyright \\u00a9 2025 Breitbart\", \"from\": 3790, \"to\": 3816, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3807, \"end\": 3816, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Breitbart_News\", \"score\": 0.9999999982460395, \"rank\": 1.7538550807228806e-09, \"text\": \"Breitbart\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Breitbart_News\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Breitbart_News\"}]}]}"